attachment.sql:
select /*SOQL*/ *
from (select t.namespace_prefix "NamespacePrefix",
t.tl_setup_entity_data_id "Id"
from core.tl_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("NamespacePrefix" is not null)

select /*SOQL*/ *
from (select (SELECT (CASE WHEN versionnumber > 1 AND status = '1' THEN '3' else status end )                                  FROM DecisionMatrixDefVerSnpsht dm                                  where dm.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI'                                  AND dm.decisionMatrixDefinitionVer_id= t.tl_setup_entity_data_id                                   AND dm.versionnumber = (SELECT max(versionnumber) FROM                                  DecisionMatrixDefVerSnpsht dm1 where dm1.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI'                                  AND dm1.decisionMatrixDefinitionVer_id = t.tl_setup_entity_data_id )) "Status",
t.std3 "ActiveVersionSnapshotId",
t.std0 "DecisionMatrixDefinitionId",
t.tl_setup_entity_data_id "Id"
from core.tl_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("Status" = ?)

select /*SOQL*/ "Id",
"DeveloperName",
"SetupName",
"Description",
"SourceObject"
from (select t.std5 "Status",
t.tl_setup_entity_data_id "Id",
t.developer_name "DeveloperName",
t.std0 "SetupName",
t.std25 "Description",
t.std4 "SourceObject"
from core.tl_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("Status" = ?)

select /*SOQL*/ *
from (select t.tl_setup_entity_data_id "Id",
t.std0 "DecisionTableId",
t.developer_name "DeveloperName",
t.std25 "Description",
t.std1 "SetupName",
t.std4 "IsDefault",
t.std3 "SourceObject"
from core.tl_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))

select /*SOQL*/ "ExpressionSetId",
"ExpressionSetDefinitionVerId",
"Name",
"Id"
from (select t.std8 "IsActive",
t.std0 "ExpressionSetId",
t.std15 "ExpressionSetDefinitionVerId",
t.name "Name",
t.standard_entity_data_id "Id"
from core.standard_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("IsActive" = '1')

select /*SOQL*/ "Id"
from (select TO_NUMBER(t.std9) "SystemVersion",
t.tl_setup_entity_data_id "Id"
from core.tl_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("SystemVersion" > ?)

select /*SOQL*/ "Id"
from (select t.std1 "Type",
t.parent_enum_or_id "SobjectType",
upper(t.developer_name) "_SORT_COL_0",
t.ent_setup_entity_data_id "Id"
from core.ent_setup_entity_data t
where (t.organization_id = '00DRO0000009YRI')
and (t.deleted = '0')
and (t.key_prefix = ?))
where ("Type" in (?, ?, ?))
order by "SobjectType" asc nulls first, "_SORT_COL_0" asc nulls first
